87     * Groups of variables to restrict.
88     *
89     * This method should be overridden in extending classes.
90     *
91     * Example: groups => array(

111    protected function setup_groups() {
112        $this->groups_cache = $this->getGroups();
113
114        if ( empty( $this->groups_cache ) && empty( self::$groups ) ) {
115            return false;
116        }
117
118        // Allow for adding extra unit tests.
119        if ( ! empty( self::$groups ) ) {
120            $this->groups_cache = array_merge( $this->groups_cache, self::$groups );
121        }

124    }

126    /**
127     * Processes this test, when one of its tokens is encountered.
128     *
129     * @param int $stackPtr The position of the current token in the stack.
130     *
131     * @return void
132     */
133    public function process_token( $stackPtr ) {
134
135        $this->excluded_groups = $this->merge_custom_array( $this->exclude );
136        if ( array_diff_key( $this->groups_cache, $this->excluded_groups ) === array() ) {
137            // All groups have been excluded.
138            // Don't remove the listener as the exclude property can be changed inline.
139            return;
140        }
141
142        $token = $this->tokens[ $stackPtr ];
143
144        if ( \T_CLOSE_SQUARE_BRACKET === $token['code'] ) {
145            $equal = $this->phpcsFile->findNext( \T_WHITESPACE, ( $stackPtr + 1 ), null, true );
146            if ( \T_EQUAL !== $this->tokens[ $equal ]['code'] ) {
147                return; // This is not an assignment!
148            }
149        }
150
151        // Instances: Multi-dimensional array, keyed by line.
152        $inst = array();
153
154        /*
155         * Covers:
156         * $foo = array( 'bar' => 'taz' );
157         * $foo['bar'] = $taz;
158         */
159        if ( \in_array( $token['code'], array( \T_CLOSE_SQUARE_BRACKET, \T_DOUBLE_ARROW ), true ) ) {
160            $operator = $stackPtr; // T_DOUBLE_ARROW.
161            if ( \T_CLOSE_SQUARE_BRACKET === $token['code'] ) {
162                $operator = $this->phpcsFile->findNext( \T_EQUAL, ( $stackPtr + 1 ) );
163            }
164
165            $keyIdx = $this->phpcsFile->findPrevious( array( \T_WHITESPACE, \T_CLOSE_SQUARE_BRACKET ), ( $operator - 1 ), null, true );
166            if ( ! is_numeric( $this->tokens[ $keyIdx ]['content'] ) ) {
167                $key            = $this->strip_quotes( $this->tokens[ $keyIdx ]['content'] );
168                $valStart       = $this->phpcsFile->findNext( array( \T_WHITESPACE ), ( $operator + 1 ), null, true );
169                $valEnd         = $this->phpcsFile->findNext( array( \T_COMMA, \T_SEMICOLON ), ( $valStart + 1 ), null, false, null, true );
170                $val            = $this->phpcsFile->getTokensAsString( $valStart, ( $valEnd - $valStart ) );
171                $val            = $this->strip_quotes( $val );
172                $inst[ $key ][] = array( $val, $token['line'] );
173            }
174        } elseif ( \in_array( $token['code'], array( \T_CONSTANT_ENCAPSED_STRING, \T_DOUBLE_QUOTED_STRING ), true ) ) {
175            // $foo = 'bar=taz&other=thing';
176            if ( preg_match_all( '#(?:^|&)([a-z_]+)=([^&]*)#i', $this->strip_quotes( $token['content'] ), $matches ) <= 0 ) {
177                return; // No assignments here, nothing to check.
178            }
179            foreach ( $matches[1] as $i => $_k ) {
180                $inst[ $_k ][] = array( $matches[2][ $i ], $token['line'] );
181            }
182        }
183
184        if ( empty( $inst ) ) {
185            return;
186        }
187
188        foreach ( $this->groups_cache as $groupName => $group ) {
189
190            if ( isset( $this->excluded_groups[ $groupName ] ) ) {
191                continue;
192            }
193
194            $callback = ( isset( $group['callback'] ) && is_callable( $group['callback'] ) ) ? $group['callback'] : array( $this, 'callback' );
195
196            foreach ( $inst as $key => $assignments ) {
197                foreach ( $assignments as $occurance ) {
198                    list( $val, $line ) = $occurance;
199
200                    if ( ! \in_array( $key, $group['keys'], true ) ) {
201                        continue;
202                    }
203
204                    $output = \call_user_func( $callback, $key, $val, $line, $group );
205
206                    if ( ! isset( $output ) || false === $output ) {
207                        continue;
208                    } elseif ( true === $output ) {
209                        $message = $group['message'];
210                    } else {
211                        $message = $output;
212                    }
213
214                    $this->addMessage(
215                        $message,
216                        $stackPtr,
217                        ( 'error' === $group['type'] ),
218                        $this->string_to_errorcode( $groupName . '_' . $key ),
219                        array( $key, $val )
220                    );
221                }
222            }
223        }
224    }
